              1000 hPa to 500 hPa thickness: 5383.00
Precipitable water [mm] for entire sounding: 9.95
</PRE>
<P>Description of the 
<A HREF="/upperair/columns.html">data columns</A>
or <A HREF="/upperair/indices.html">sounding indices</A>.
